data.actual_result: The icons 'hide' behind the image, becoming unclickable. (This only occurs at lower screen resolutions and at smaller window sizes.)
data.expected_result: The emoticon and triple dot icon should disappear or go above the image.
data.short_description: Emoticon and triple dot icons go behind image when search dialog opened.
data.steps_to_repro: - Open the search dialog in the top-right of Discord. - Search for an Image. (has:image) - Select "JUMP" on that image. - Hover over the image, you will notice the icons are now partially or fully obfuscated.
